id: pm-3mna
title: "Promote schema, config, profile, and init primitives to the public SDK: full workspace customization programmatically"
description: "Typed SDK functions for runtime-schema management (types/statuses/fields/presets), settings read/write with validation, profile list/show/apply/lint, and workspace init/scaffold — completing the universal-customization story. Duplicate check: profile-presets/plan are partially exported already; this item completes and stabilizes the domain surface."
type: Feature
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[4]: architecture,"area:config","area:schema","area:sdk"
created_at: "2026-07-05T04:54:11.971Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-15T01:16:44.305Z"
assignee: codex-root
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 360
acceptance_criteria: SDK exports typed schema/config/profile/init primitives with the same validation + never-block errors as the CLI; corresponding commands consume only these primitives; docstrings + linked tests + SDK reference docs; zero behavior change
parent: pm-usfg
risk: medium
confidence: medium
